               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840526-18-person228">
                  JOHN
                   WAINWRIGHT
               <interp inst="t17840526-18-person228" type="surname" value="WAINWRIGHT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-18-person228" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-18-person228" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am constable of Allhallows; going down Bush-lane, the prisoner had a sack on his back, on seeing me he dropped the sack and run away, I ran after him and cried out stop thief.</p>

               <p>What did you find in the sack? - A lead pipe and chissel.</p>
               <p>What did he say for himself? - He said he picked it up.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840526-18-person229">
                  NATHANIEL
                   COLLINS
               <interp inst="t17840526-18-person229" type="surname" value="COLLINS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-18-person229" type="given" value="NATHANIEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-18-person229" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I know the property, it belongs to my master.</p>
               <p>How do you know it? - I have known it fourteen years, it belongs to a cistern that waters the horses, fastened by a lock and chain, it slips in a socket.</p>
               <p>Was it tried whether it fitted that socket? - Yes, I fitted it, it sits it perfectly well.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was coming out of the yard, and found the sick, but the lead was in the sack, and the gentleman took me to the watch-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840526-18-verdict100" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840526-18-verdict100" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840526-18-punish101" type="punishmentDescription">
